{"id":680667,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/680667.html","date":"2022-05-02T18:27:04Z","modified":"2022-05-02T18:28:12Z","title":"【CDTV】微信频道@喵姐爱教书：别再叫羊了！","content":"<div style=\"width:42%;float:right;padding-left:20px;\">\n<div class=\"su-spoiler su-spoiler-style-fancy su-spoiler-icon-chevron-circle\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\" data-anchor-in-url=\"no\"><div class=\"su-spoiler-title\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"su-spoiler-icon\"></span>CDT 档案卡</div><div class=\"su-spoiler-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim\">\n<strong>标题：</strong>【CDTV】微信频道@喵姐爱教书：别再叫羊了！<br />\n<strong>作者：</strong>@喵姐爱教书<br />\n<strong>发表日期：</strong>2022.5.2<br />\n<strong>来源：</strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RAuvZdpd7b0&t=223s&ab_channel=404%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E9%A6%86\" target=\"_blank\">微信频道@喵姐爱教书</a><br>\n<strong>主题归类：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85\" target=\"_blank\">新冠疫情</a><br>\n<strong>CDS收藏：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E8%AF%9D%E8%AF%AD%E9%A6%86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">话语馆</a><br>\n<strong>版权说明：</strong>该作品版权归原作者所有。中国数字时代仅对原作进行存档，以对抗中国的网络审查。<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/copyright\">详细版权说明</a>。\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<p>4月30日，微信频道博主@喵姐爱教书 发布了一条视频，阐述了将新冠阳性患者叫“羊”这一做法的危险性：这是“路西法效应”的雏形。</p>\n<p>路西法效应是“斯坦福监狱实验”的设计和实施者、美国心理学家Philip Zimbardo根据这一实验的发现总结而成的理论。这个理论揭示了一个普通人是如何在某些特定的条件下变成一个恶人或公权机器下的屠杀者。</p>\n<p>这些条件包括：1. 盲从 + 极端；2. 集体 + 匿名。3. 异化（比如，把人叫羊）。</p>\n<p>截至目前，这一视频已被转发近4万次，点赞四万次。</p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"微信频道@喵姐爱教书：别再叫羊了！\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RAuvZdpd7b0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n","author":1052,"categories":[18271,43134,41492,38912,38927],"tags":[24371,39920,45342,45359]}